Oh, Emma, I missed you so much. Hi.
哦，艾犸，我真是太想你了，嗨！

302
00:22:48,330 --> 00:22:51,160
Did you have a good time with Grandma Greene? Huh?
嘿……你和姥姥过得开心吗？呃？

303
00:22:51,330 --> 00:22:55,320
Did she give you a bottle of antidepressants again to use as a rattle?
她喋喋不休的时候给你兴奋剂了吗？

304
00:22:56,700 --> 00:23:00,300
That was one time, Ross, and they were only, like, five milligrams.
只有一次，罗斯，而且只有5毫克。

305
00:23:02,180 --> 00:23:06,810
Hey, Emma, Daddy has some presents for you, okay? I want you to wait right here.
噢，嘿，艾犸，爸爸有礼物带给你。 知道吗？ 我想让你在这儿等一会儿

306
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,710
Come here, sweetie.
等等，宝贝儿。

307
00:23:09,850 --> 00:23:14,150
Ross, actually, there's something that I really need to talk to you about.
呃……罗斯 事实上我有点儿事要跟你说。

308
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:16,020
Okay, shoot.
好的，说吧！

309
00:23:16,190 --> 00:23:21,820
- Okay. All right, here's the deal. - Oh, no!
- 好吧，呃……好的，事情是这样的。 - 哦不！

310
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:27,990
- What is it? - Oh, major shampoo explosion!
- 怎么了？那是什么？ - 噢，大瓶的洗发液破了！

311
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:33,660
- Look, Ross, this really isn't easy. - Oh, it's all over everything!
- 呃，听着罗斯，这很难开口。 - 啊！！还沾得到处都是。

312
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,570
Why? Why me?
为什么？为什么偏偏是我？

313
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:42,550
Because you took 300 bottles of shampoo?
因为你拿了300瓶洗发液？

314
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:47,080
I guess things were just going too well for me.
我猜这些东西对我来说太珍贵了.

315
00:23:48,490 --> 00:23:50,750
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. You were saying?
对不起，对不起。你刚才说什么？

316
00:23:51,090 --> 00:23:56,290
- Well, yeah. Look, it's about me and.. - Oh, not another one!
- 好吧，呃……好吧，听着，是关于我和…… - 噢，不要，又一瓶！？

317
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:02,570
Oh, my God.. Oh, and this is moisturizer! It's even harder to clean!
噢，天……是摩丝。这个更难清理！

318
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:07,800
Why? Why do bad things happen to good people?
为什么？为什么坏事总是落到好人的头上？

319
00:24:09,810 --> 00:24:14,300
- Wow. Clearly this is not a good time. - You think?
- 哇！好吧，很显然这不是个好时候。 - 嗯，你觉得呢？！

320
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:20,150
Okay. Bye.
好的，再见。

321
00:24:20,320 --> 00:24:23,590
All right, so Mike's on his way over.
好了，麦克已经回来了。

322
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:27,780
You thought you were meeting here, he thought at the restaurant, so..
知道吗，你以为你们在这儿见 他却以为在餐馆见面 所以……

323
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:32,260
It doesn't matter who's right or wrong. The point is, I'm gonna take off.
谁对谁错不重要 重要的是…… 我要走了。

324
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:37,330
Wait. I'm not letting you leave until you tell me what's going on. I mean..
你告诉我到底发生了什么之前 我不会让你走的。

325
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:39,970
are you guys getting back together or something?
我是说，你们和好了还是怎么了？

326
00:24:41,340 --> 00:24:43,040
All right.
好吧……

327
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:47,910
Susie.. Can I call you Susie?
苏茜，我能叫你苏茜吗？

328
00:24:48,450 --> 00:24:50,440
My name is Precious.
我叫Precious。

329
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:53,450
I can't say that.
对，可我叫不出口。

330
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:57,780
Susie, I'm gonna be straight with you.
呃……Susie，我想跟你直说……

331
00:24:58,190 --> 00:25:02,180
Mike and I are back together. And unfortunately..
麦克和我和好了…… 并且，呃……不幸的是

332
00:25:02,360 --> 00:25:06,060
that effectively ends your relationship with him.
这样就要终结你们的关系。

333
00:25:06,230 --> 00:25:12,930
He's very sorry about that, and wishes you the best luck in all your endeavors.
并且他对此感到很抱歉，并祝你好运。

334
00:25:14,070 --> 00:25:17,510
I just can't believe this. Why?
我无法相信……为什么？

335
00:25:17,780 --> 00:25:19,770
- Well, I don't.. - Why would he do this?
- 这个我也不知…… - 噢，他为什么这么做？

336
00:25:19,950 --> 00:25:22,680
- What's wrong with me? - There's nothing wrong with you.
- 我做错什么了？ - 没有，你什么也没做错。

337
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:24,940
What the hell am I supposed to do now?
我是说，现在我到底该做什么？

338
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:28,350
Damn it, woman! Pull yourself together!
可恶！你这女人，镇定点，镇定。

339
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:31,620
Have some pride, for the love of God!
保持你的尊严，看在上帝的份上！

340
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:39,160
Okay, not a fan of the tough love.
好吧，你好象不喜欢苦涩的爱情。

341
00:25:39,370 --> 00:25:43,200
I just can't believe that Mike didn't give me any warning.
我真不明白，为什么他不给我点暗示在先呢！

342
00:25:43,370 --> 00:25:48,430
He didn't know. He wasn't planning on coming to Barbados and proposing to me.
他之前也不知道的 他本来没计划到巴贝多向我求婚的……

343
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:53,980
He proposed to you? This is the worst birthday ever!
他向你求婚了？ 我这个生日真是糟透了。

344
00:25:57,850 --> 00:26:01,050
Look, Precious..
听着，Precious……

345
00:26:03,190 --> 00:26:07,060
Mike's not worth this. You're an attractive, intelligent woman..
你不值为麦克伤心。 你是个迷人的、聪明的女孩

346
00:26:07,230 --> 00:26:09,720
and let's face it, Mike's kind of a wang.
你看 麦克简直有点混蛋。

347
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,960
He proposed to me while he was still seeing you.
我是说 他向我求婚的时候甚至还跟你在一起……

348
00:26:14,170 --> 00:26:16,860
He was gonna break up with you on your birthday?
他居然想在你生日的时候跟你分手？

349
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:21,910
I don't like to kiss and tell, but he cheated on you a lot this weekend.
并且，我本来也不想说的 不过这个周末他对你不忠的太多了。

350
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:25,340
Oh, my God, you know, maybe you're right. Maybe I don't need him.
噢，天呐，可能你说对了。 可能我并不需要他。

351
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:28,500
I deserve to be treated with respect.
我应该受到尊重。

352
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:34,780
Screw you, Mike. You're a coward and a bastard, and I hope you rot in hell!
你这个混蛋，麦克。 你这个胆怯的杂种，我希望你烂死在地狱里。

353
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:42,120
You're welcome.
不用谢我！

354
00:26:47,270 --> 00:26:51,290
Honey? You've been in there for a long time. Is everything okay?
亲爱的，你在里面好久了……没事吧？

355
00:26:51,500 --> 00:26:53,400
Not really.
有一点事。

356
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:57,670
I have a problem.
我出事了。

357
00:26:58,350 --> 00:27:01,440
Really? What happened?
是吗？怎么了？

358
00:27:01,650 --> 00:27:07,140
Well, I was dancing around and singing "No Woman, No Cry"..
好吧，我唱着《No Woman, No Cry》跳舞...

359
00:27:09,090 --> 00:27:11,280
and I got stuck.
然后就挂住了。

360
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:15,290
- You can't move at all? - Oh, I can move.
- 一点都动不了？ - 噢，不，我可以动……

361
00:27:21,370 --> 00:27:24,340
If I untangle you, will you please get rid of the cornrows?
如果我解开你，你会解开这个稻穗头？

362
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,440
I guess so.
我想会……

363
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:32,810
- Some of these look a little frayed. - Yeah, I tried to gnaw myself free.
- 有些看起来缠在一起了。 - 对，我自己试着解开过。

364
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,140
- Hey. - Hi.
- 嗨！ - 嗨！

365
00:27:38,390 --> 00:27:41,880
- So? Did you tell Ross? - Well, I tried..
- 呃……你跟罗斯说了吗？ - 没有，我想说

366
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:45,220
but then he had a shampoo-related emergency.
但他的洗发液出事故了。

367
00:27:45,930 --> 00:27:48,450
- So I guess now it's your turn again. - No, no, no, no.
- 所以我想该轮到你去了。 - 不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不……

368
00:27:48,630 --> 00:27:52,120
I think it's better if you tell him. You know, it's easier for a woman.
我想最好是你去告诉他，知道吗  这对女人来说容易些。

369
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:55,390
That way, you know, if he gets mad, all you have to do is go:
你知道，如果他抓狂了 你就可以……

370
00:27:55,570 --> 00:27:57,800
"I didn't mean it.
我不是有意的。

371
00:27:59,170 --> 00:28:02,300
I'm so sorry."
我太抱歉了。

372
00:28:04,910 --> 00:28:06,850
Yeah, because that's what we do.
对，我们的确会这么做的

373
00:28:07,250 --> 00:28:12,280
All right, all right, okay. How about this? How about this? Tomorrow..
好吧，好吧，这样，呃……这样，这样怎么样？

374
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:16,240
Tomorrow we'll both go and we'll tell him together.
明天……明天我们一起去，一起告诉他。

375
00:28:16,420 --> 00:28:18,120
Okay, that sounds fair.
好吧，听起来公平些。

376
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:21,090
- That just means, once again, we can't.. - I know.
- 可这样我们又不能…… - 我知道，我知道……

377
00:28:21,260 --> 00:28:25,130
That's okay. I mean, we can control ourselves. We're not animals.
不过没问题。 我们有自制力，我们不是动物啊。

378
00:28:25,330 --> 00:28:29,320
- No! Of course, we can wait. - Yeah.
- 当然，当然我们可以等。 - 是啊。

379
00:28:29,970 --> 00:28:32,340
All right, so I guess that means good night then.
那么我想该说晚安了？

380
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:35,300
Yep. Good night.
好的！晚安！

381
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:43,970
Good night.
晚――安！

382
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,980
Good night.
晚安！

383
00:28:53,630 --> 00:28:56,390
- Seriously, good night. - Stop saying good night.
- 说真的，晚安！ - 别说晚安了。

384
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:20,110
I'm so sorry.
好的。真对不起啊...

385
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:28,290
Look what I found in the drawer.
看我在抽屉里找到了什么……

386
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:33,430
And you said I'd never wear this.
你还说我永远不会戴它呢。

387
00:29:34,330 --> 00:29:37,930
Now that I untangled you, how about you do a little something for me?
我把你解救下来，你还没报答我呢？

388
00:29:38,100 --> 00:29:41,870
- Sure. What did you have in mind? - I think you know.
-当然，你想让我怎么报答？ - 你应该知道的啊。

389
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:47,210
- Really? I don't.. I don't really feel like it. - This is what I want to do.
- 真的？但我有点不想啊。 - 我就是想要。

390
00:29:48,210 --> 00:29:49,770
Okay.
好吧。

391
00:29:50,020 --> 00:29:53,320
I just don't get why you like it so much.
我不知道你为什么这么喜欢它。

392
00:29:53,490 --> 00:29:56,980
She's an FBI agent posing as a beauty contestant!
她是个FBI特工，还参加选美呢。

393
